Package structures.commons

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataStructure<T>
    Generic interface for any data structure in this library.
    IndexedDataStructure<T>
    Abstract IndexedDataStructure structure.
    LinearDataStructure<T>
    Interface for all linear DataStructures such as LinkedList, ArrayList, or any other vector-like data structure.
    Value<T>
    Generic Value class to be extended from by classes such as Nodes in LinkedLists or Edges and vertexes in Graphs.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChainedDataStructure<T>
    Abstract class to be implemented by all types of LinkedLists, and data structures that are dynamically size, but we do not know how many elements we will start with / have.
    ChainedDataStructure.ChainedDataStructureIterator<T>
    Iterates over a ChainedDataStructure via pointers
    ChainedDataStructure.Node<T>
    Node class for chaining together values in a LinkedList
    ChainedIndexedDataStructure<T>  
    DynamicallySizedArray<T>
    Incomplete class that should be implemented by classes that have growing arrays in the back.
    DynamicallySizedDataStructure<T>
    All dynamically sized data types should extend this class
    IndexedDataStructure.IndexedDataStructureIterator<T>
    Static Iterator class so that the IndexedDataStructure can be iterated on via the enhance for loop
    Pair<K,V>
    Key-value pair object for use in Objects such as Maps and Trees.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DataStructure.EmptyDataStructureException
    Exception that is throw when an operation takes places that requires the DataStructure to be non-empty, but its empty.
